"{\"uid\": \"nbnnews.com.au-2024-07-29-nnsw-olympic-wrap-molly-picklums-run-comes-to-an-end-in-tahiti\", \"text\": \"Our chances of surfing gold were dealt a huge blow this morning, with the Central Coast's Molly Picklum eliminated in the second round in Tahiti.  Australian sporting officials have since called for a review of Olympic rules\\u2026 after Pickum was seeded well below her current world ranking.\"}"